OL,5, Lord Alan Sugar said he was "always    
OL,6, looking over my shoulder" and worried  
OL,7, about the safety of his family after   
OL,8, receiving anti-Semitic letters.        
OL,10,FThree letters, including one saying "I 
OL,11,Fwould like to murder all Jews in       
OL,12,FBritain, Alan" were sent to business   
OL,13,Fpremises in Loughton, Essex  in 2018.  
OL,15,FPatrick Gomes, 70, was jailed for three
OL,16,Fyears and six months at Chelmsford     
OL,17,FCrown Court.                           
OL,19,FLord Sugar said the letters had "shaken
OL,20,Fme up".                                
